data.description: Single family all brick home. Large screened in back porch. In ground salt water pool. Large drive way extended out to the road. Whole home Culligan water purification system. Fire pit, in-ground sprinkler system. Outdoor Kitchen with gas and hot/cold water ran to it with a sink, refrigerator, single burner, large gas grill, with large ceiling fan. If you are looking for a country oasis with plenty of wildlife, this is the place for you.
data.whatILove: This home is located in the perfect area. It is not on a main road. Very quiet location.
